<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Progresso Semanal | PlanoB</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/progressosemanal.css">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lexend:wght@300;400;600;700;800&family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <header class="topo">
        <a href="/painelfree" class="logo">PlanoB</a>

        <nav class="menu-desktop">
            <a href="/painelfree">Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/videosfree">Vídeos</a>
            <a href="/progressosemanal" class="ativo">Evolução</a>
            <a href="/streakprogress">Streak</a>
        </nav>

        <nav class="acoes-topo">
            <a href="/streakprogress" aria-label="Streak">
                <i class="material-symbols-outlined">local_fire_department</i>
            </a>

            <a href="/suporte" aria-label="Suporte">
                <i class="material-symbols-outlined">support_agent</i>
            </a>

            <a href="/painelfree" class="avatar" aria-label="Perfil">
                <img src="/img/profile.png" alt="Foto de perfil">
            </a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="conteudo">
        <section class="cabecalho-pagina">
            <article class="brilho"></article>

            <h1>
                Seu fluxo
                <strong>de evolução</strong>
            </h1>

            <p>
                Análise detalhada da sua performance semanal.
                Você está <strong>12% melhor</strong> que na semana passada.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="grade-principal">
            <article class="card grafico-card">
                <header class="card-cabecalho">
                    <article>
                        <h2>Tempo de Treino</h2>

                        <p>
                            Segunda a Domingo
                            <strong>+4.5% de aumento</strong>
                        </p>
                    </article>

                    <aside>
                        <strong>342 min</strong>
                        <p>+15m vs. média anterior</p>
                    </aside>
                </header>

                <section class="grafico">
                    <ol class="linhas-grafico">
                        <li>100m</li>
                        <li>75m</li>
                        <li>50m</li>
                        <li>25m</li>
                        <li>0m</li>
                    </ol>

                    <ol class="barras-grafico">
                        <li>
                            <meter min="0" max="100" value="42">42 minutos</meter>
                            <abbr title="Segunda-feira">Seg</abbr>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <meter min="0" max="100" value="65">65 minutos</meter>
                            <abbr title="Terça-feira">Ter</abbr>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <meter min="0" max="100" value="50">50 minutos</meter>
                            <abbr title="Quarta-feira">Qua</abbr>
                        </li>

                        <li class="destaque">
                            <meter min="0" max="100" value="85">85 minutos</meter>
                            <abbr title="Quinta-feira">Qui</abbr>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <meter min="0" max="100" value="70">70 minutos</meter>
                            <abbr title="Sexta-feira">Vie</abbr>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <meter min="0" max="100" value="30">30 minutos</meter>
                            <abbr title="Sábado">Sáb</abbr>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <meter min="0" max="100" value="20">20 minutos</meter>
                            <abbr title="Domingo">Dom</abbr>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </section>
            </article>

            <aside class="coluna-lateral">
                <article class="card ofensiva-card">
                    <i class="material-symbols-outlined icone-fundo">local_fire_department</i>

                    <p class="tag-card">
                        <i class="material-symbols-outlined">trending_up</i>
                        Ofensiva atual
                    </p>

                    <h2>Sua ofensiva</h2>

                    <p>
                        Você está imparável! Mantenha o ritmo para desbloquear novas recompensas.
                    </p>

                    <strong>42</strong>

                    <small>Dias seguidos</small>
                </article>

                <article class="card beneficios-card">
                    <header>
                        <h2>Benefícios ativos</h2>
                        <a href="/streakprogress">Ver todos</a>
                    </header>

                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <i class="material-symbols-outlined">percent</i>

                            <article>
                                <h3>15% OFF Whey Protein</h3>
                                <p>Resgatado</p>
                            </article>
                        </li>

                        <li class="bloqueado">
                            <i class="material-symbols-outlined">lock</i>

                            <article>
                                <h3>Cupom Centauro R$ 50</h3>
                                <p>Faltam 3 dias</p>
                            </article>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
            </aside>

            <article class="card frequencia-card">
                <header>
                    <i class="material-symbols-outlined">fitness_center</i>

                    <article>
                        <p>Frequência</p>
                        <h2>08 Treinos</h2>
                    </article>
                </header>

                <section>
                    <header>
                        <p>Meta semanal</p>
                        <strong>80% concluído</strong>
                    </header>

                    <progress max="100" value="80">80%</progress>

                    <p>Faltam 2 treinos para bater a meta</p>
                </section>
            </article>

            <article class="card analise-card">
                <figure class="anel-progresso">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 180 180" aria-label="Evolução de 12%">
                        <defs>
                            <linearGradient id="gradienteAnel" x1="0%" x2="100%" y1="0%" y2="100%">
                                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0058ba"></stop>
                                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#6c9fff"></stop>
                            </linearGradient>
                        </defs>

                        <circle cx="90" cy="90" r="76"></circle>
                        <circle cx="90" cy="90" r="76"></circle>
                    </svg>

                    <figcaption>
                        <strong>+12%</strong>
                        <small>Evolução</small>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>

                <section>
                    <h2>Análise de rendimento</h2>

                    <p>
                        Seu volume de treino aumentou consideravelmente em comparação com a semana passada.
                        Foco mantido nos <strong>membros superiores</strong> com ganho de
                        <strong>5% em força explosiva</strong>.
                    </p>

                    <nav class="botoes-card">
                        <a href="/progressosemanal">
                            Ver detalhes
                            <i class="material-symbols-outlined">insights</i>
                        </a>

                        <a href="#">
                            Relatório PDF
                            <i class="material-symbols-outlined">download</i>
                        </a>
                    </nav>
                </section>
            </article>
        </section>

        <section class="desafios">
            <article class="desafios-texto">
                <h2>
                    Seu próximo
                    <strong>desafio</strong>
                </h2>

                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/videosfree">
                            <i class="material-symbols-outlined">bolt</i>

                            <article>
                                <h3>HIIT Power Blast</h3>
                                <p>45 minutos • Foco em queima calórica</p>
                            </article>

                            <strong>Intenso</strong>

                            <i class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward_ios</i>
                        </a>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <a href="/videosfree">
                            <i class="material-symbols-outlined">self_improvement</i>

                            <article>
                                <h3>Yoga Flow Matinal</h3>
                                <p>30 minutos • Flexibilidade e mobilidade</p>
                            </article>

                            <strong>Médio</strong>

                            <i class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward_ios</i>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <figure class="desafio-imagem">
                <img src="/img/treino-recomendado.jpg" alt="Pessoa treinando com halteres">

                <figcaption>
                    <small>Recomendado hoje</small>
                    <strong>Superação nos halteres</strong>
                </figcaption>

                <aside>
                    <i class="material-symbols-outlined">auto_awesome</i>

                    <article>
                        <p>Smart Pick</p>
                        <strong>Baseado na sua semana</strong>
                    </article>
                </aside>
            </figure>
